title: [LFG] New player seeking gaming community to join.
body: Basically looking for a new community to join, I was once part of another group which was international and ignored the Oceanic section, so I am looking for a new place to call home and have fun with other players, and hopefully get better at the game when I hit level 30 within ranked.
